Package com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.model

Classes as models for mock objects within EC2.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMockEc2Instance
    Generic class for mock ec2 instance, with basic simulation of behaviors and states of genuine ec2 instances' life cycle.
    DefaultMockEc2Instance
    Default type of mock ec2 instance (extends AbstractMockEc2Instance).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AbstractMockEc2Instance.InstanceState
    Enumeration of all instance states.
    AbstractMockEc2Instance.InstanceType
    Enumeration of all allowed instance types.
